desc: Beer Garden Table Vintage German 3pc Set for Outdoor Dining at Restaurants, Pubs, Orchards, Vineyards, Wedding Venues. Great for wine tastings and breweries as well as hosting your own Oktoberfest or for home use on the patio. The Table and Benches fold flat and are collapsible for easy transportation & storage.

layout.text: Made with precision German engineering and construction, our Oktoberfest tables & benches are imported directly from Germany from a variety of breweries in the Bavaria Region. We have provided hundreds of customers with an affordable and nostalgic outdoor dining classic.
